Program: Outlook
Title: Rattlesnake Derby
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrjx
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
A visit to Mangum, Oklahoma for the annual Rattlesnake Derby. Also, a look inside some bento lunch boxes in Japan. Schemes for dealing with post traumatic stress disorder in soldiers, including an interview with Denzil Connick. Finally, searching for unicorns. Presenter: Frederick Dove.